{
  "texts": [
    "The integration of AI into sensory-driven food design enables scalable, data-driven decision-making.",
    "This contributes to shorter development cycles, improved consumer targeting, and more sustainable product pipelines.",
    "As AI technologies mature, their role in creating food products that are both delicious and aligned with health and environmental goals is expected to grow.",
    "The convergence of neuroscience, AI, and food science is expected to play a key role in advancing sensory research.",
    "Flavor perception involves complex brain processes that are not yet fully understood."
  ]
}